t<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b29ff88b627428ae9d328440e66b17ffc1713e02","tid":95352,"uid":43589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T04:51:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁愛國就咪去日本啦</blockquote>"},{"pid":"e867a00ec89a382a0f5052d338bfc26c0064f0d7","tid":95352,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T04:59:43.000Z","msg":"支那人真係低智<br />\n要懲罰APA最好既方法唔係抵制<br />\n而係派蝗軍book爆APA啲酒店<br />\n然後去瀨屎瀨尿"},{"pid":"0b6e80648d9ac7aaa4df6938593b4bb2dc534370","tid":95352,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T05:07:42.000Z","msg":"老闆都知道， 逢支那人講抵制杯葛都係得啖笑<br />\n好快就唔記得， 支那人邊撚到有骨氣㗎"},{"pid":"fc4cf4a3685fea2e11d5109a012d2b5c49b0c21b","tid":95352,"uid":28155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T05:08:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>&quot;無中國人入住&quot;呢個根本就係神級selling point<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}